>
>When I started the wipers, the gas gauge started "wiping" as well.

I agree with Clara: check the ground at the gas gauge.  You might also
check the ground wire at the wiper motor.  If you have a '66-up with
extra fancy two speed self parking wipers, also check the ground at
the wiper switch; it grounds through its mounting to the dash.

Matt Roberds
